userstories: A farmer has to submit the land details, their survey number , 
total land in hectors and village name to the bank.
The bank creates a portal using these details and this portal is accessed by the farmers who are registered.

Approval of loan: As a farmer i need to send the details of the land that i had in hectors . 
Based on that the loan is sancioned to me.

Loan Registration:Loan is registered through the portal and in that portal farmer has to provide their
 land details and type of cultivation.
MILESTONES:
    1. CLEAR OF LOANS AND UPDATE DETAILS IN PORTAL.
    2.REGISTER AND VIEW DETAILS.
    3.GOVERNMENT MAY ALSO TRANSFER MONEY FOR ANY SUBSIDY /INSURABNCE AMOUNT TO AADHAR LINKED BANK ACCOUNT.
